These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, traveling, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, crime, thriller
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person watching scientific movies##6
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | board-games   | gardening    | woodworking    | traveling |
| Sport      | thriller | scientific | crime | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
City: london, hamburg, san-francisco, liverpool
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bolivar, old-henry, vegafina
1. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
3. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
4. the person traveling to hamburg is not the bolivar-smoker##6
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | hamburg  | san-francisco    | london | liverpool    |
| Food       | vegafina | bolivar | old-henry  | cain |

