.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cauliflower, cranberry, cucumber
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, apricot, purple, ivory
1. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
3. the person who likes ivory is not the person eating cauliflower##6
4. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
6. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | cauliflower | cranberry | cucumber     | plum |
| Transport   | apricot     | purple    | turquise | ivory    |

