2. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
4. the person who likes black is not the colonial house##6
5. the art-deco house is not the person who likes ebony##6
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes black##1
7. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | ebony        | turquise | aquamarine | black |
| Transport   | colonial | art-deco | cape-cod     | cottage   |

