.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, frog, goldfish
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, pineapple, plum, artichoke
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is not the person eating pineapple##6
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
5. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
7. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
8. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
9. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | pony | frog    | guinea-pig  | goldfish   |
| Nationality   | plum  | artichoke | pineapple | pumpkin |

