The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the electrician##6
3. the manager is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
6. the electrician is the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | freelancer | electrician     | mechanic | manager |
| Music-Genre   | ice-hockey | rugby | weightlifting      | volleyball         |

