.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, surfing, handball
1. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking juice is not the person who's sport is handball##6
8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | juice  | 7up | sprite    | mirinda |
| Transport   | swimming | handball | surfing | cycling  |

