3. the person who growsbellflower is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who likes green is not the person who growsbellflower##6
6. the person who growsaconite is not the person who likes red##6
7. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes green is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
