.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, guinea-pig, lizard
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, traveling, skydiving, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is not the owner of the horse##6
5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | horse | fish | lizard      | guinea-pig   |
| Transport   | hiking  | traveling   | skydiving | chess |

 